OL,3,CHospital declares 'critical incident'
OL,4,Cas hundreds seek emergency care
OL,6,FDerriford Hospital in Plymouth has
OL,7,Fdeclared a critical incident due to
OL,8,Fincreased pressure on its emergency
OL,9,Fdepartment.
OL,11,FMore than 300 people attended the
OL,12,Fhospital needing emergency treatment
OL,13,Fon Monday, almost 200 of whom were
OL,14,Fadmitted as inpatients.
OL,16,FPeople accompanying patients have been
OL,17,Fasked not to enter the emergency
OL,18,Fdepartment unless absolutely necessary.
