OL,6,FThe trust said it is seeing high
OL,7,Fnumbers of older patients with
OL,8,Frespiratory problems exacerbated by
OL,9,Fthe cold weather.
OL,11,FThe trust's chief nurse, Darryn
OL,12,FAllcorn, said: "Our Emergency
OL,13,FDepartment is there for life-
OL,14,Fthreatening conditions and real
OL,15,Femergencies.
