OL,6,F"If you can use other services, such
OL,7,Fas NHS 111, pharmacy or your GP,
OL,8,Fplease do so. If you do come to the
OL,9,Femergency department and it is not an
OL,10,Femergency or a life-threatening
OL,11,Fcondition, then you may be redirected.
OL,13,F"It's really important we make sure
OL,14,Fthat the sickest patients are
OL,15,Fprioritised and that we keep our
OL,16,Fservices flowing for those who are in
OL,17,Fgreatest need.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
