OL,6,F"Therefore, we ask that at this time
OL,7,Funless you are a carer or if the
OL,8,Fpatient who is coming to the hospital
OL,9,Fis particularly distressed, that those
OL,10,Fwho accompany patients do not to come
OL,11,Finto the emergency department. We need
OL,12,Fthe seating spaces for patients to sit
OL,13,Fdown and be comfortable.
OL,15,F"We ask that patients, visitors and
OL,16,Ffamilies be kind to one another and
OL,17,Fcontinue to treat staff with respect
OL,18,Fduring this extremely busy period."
