OL,3,CHospital declares 'critical incident'
OL,4,Cas hundreds seek emergency care
OL,6,FLast week the NHS in Cornwall declared
OL,7,Fa critical incident and issued an
OL,8,Furgent warning to residents due to
OL,9,F"sustained pressure" on the Royal
OL,10,FCornwall Hospital.
OL,12,FIt allows the NHS to take "additional,
OL,13,Fimmediate steps to create capacity,
OL,14,Fdischarge patients, relieve pressure
OL,15,Fon (the) emergency department and
OL,16,Frelease ambulances and their crews",
OL,17,Faccording to NHS Cornwall and Isles of
OL,18,FScilly Integrated Care Board (ICB).
OL,26,@wD@DpmwD@Hpn
