OL,3,CHospital declares 'critical incident'
OL,4,Cas hundreds seek emergency care
OL,6,FIt comes after health bosses warned
OL,7,Ffreezing temperatures at the beginning
OL,8,Fof January could put additional strain
OL,9,Fon the NHS, with a four-fold increase
OL,10,Fin people being admitted for flu
OL,11,Fnationally.
OL,13,FKate Shields, the ICB's chief
OL,14,Fexecutive, said: "We are currently
OL,15,Fseeing a high number of ambulances
OL,16,Fwaiting outside the Royal Cornwall
OL,17,FHospital and of patients in our
OL,18,Femergency department.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
