OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F432A1736255264
OL,3,CHospital declares 'critical incident'
OL,4,Cas hundreds seek emergency care
OL,6,F"There are also a large number of
OL,7,Fpatients in Cornwall's hospitals who
OL,8,Fare medically fit to be discharged but
OL,9,Fare awaiting the right care.
OL,11,F"We urgently need the public's support
OL,12,Fto make sure we can see those who are
OL,13,Fsickest and have the greatest need."
OL,15,FDr Chris Reid, dhief medical officer
OL,16,Ffor NHS Cornwall and the Isles of
OL,17,FScilly Integrated Care Board, said:
OL,18,F"Over the last month we have seen
OL,19,Falmost four times as many hospital
OL,20,Finpatients with flu as we did a year
OL,21,Fago.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
