OL,3,CHospital declares 'critical incident'
OL,4,Cas hundreds seek emergency care
OL,6,F"Calling a system critical incident
OL,7,Fallows us to stand down non urgent
OL,8,Fwork and focus on seeing more patients
OL,9,Fin our primary care hubs, getting
OL,10,Fpeople home from hospital and helping
OL,11,Fkeep them from needing to be admitted.
OL,13,F"I want to thank all of our
OL,14,Fhardworking colleagues across the
OL,15,Fhealth and care system who work
OL,16,Ftirelessly all year round but are
OL,17,Funder particular pressure when our
OL,18,Fservices are so busy."
